\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 \uc0\u272 \'e2y l\'e0 m\u7897 t trong nh\u7919 ng\'a0c\'e2u ca dao t\u7909 c ng\u7919  n\'f3i v\u7873  c\'f4ng cha ngh\u297 a m\u7865  \u417 n th\u7847 y hay v\'e0 \'fd ngh\u297 a. Ch\u7881  v\u7899 i v\'e0i t\u7915  ng\u7855 n g\u7885 n nh\u432 ng c\'e2u ca dao \u273 \'e3 nh\u7855 c nh\u7903  ch\'fang ta ph\u7843 i lu\'f4n bi\u7871 t ghi nh\u7899  c\'f4ng lao c\u7911 a cha m\u7865 , c\'f4ng \u417 n d\u7841 y d\u7895  c\u7911 a th\u7847 y c\'f4.*
\f0\b\fs36 C\'f4ng cha ngh\uc0\u297 a m\u7865  \u417 n th\u7847 y. Ng\'e0y sau kh\'f4n l\u7899 n \u417 n d\'e0y bi\u7875 n s\'e2u.\

\f1\b0\fs32 C\'e2u ca dao tr\'ean c\uc0\u361 ng l\'e0 l\u7901 i r\u259 n d\u7841 y m\u7895 i ch\'fang ta ph\u7843 i lu\'f4n lu\'f4n kh\u7855 c ghi c\'f4ng \u417 n c\u7911 a nh\u7919 ng ng\u432 \u7901 i \u273 \'e3 c\'f3 c\'f4ng sinh th\'e0nh, nu\'f4i d\u7841 y ch\'fang ta tr\u432 \u7903 ng th\'e0nh. Cha m\u7865  cho ta h\'ecnh h\'e0i, cho ta cu\u7897 c s\u7889 ng \u7845 m no, cho ta \u273 \u432 \u7907 c \u259 n \u273 \u432 \u7907 c h\u7885 c, c\'f2n th\u7847 y c\'f4 cho ta ki\u7871 n th\u7913 c, d\u7841 y ta nh\u7919 ng \u273 i\u7873 u b\u7893  \'edch. C\'f4ng lao \u7845 y c\u7911 a cha, c\u7911 a m\u7865 , c\u7911 a ng\u432 \u7901 i th\u7847 y l\u7899 n lao t\u7921 a tr\u7901 i b\u7875 , d\'f9 \u273 i \u273 \'e2u, l\'e0m g\'ec th\'ec m\u7895 i ch\'fang ta v\u7851 n ph\u7843 i kh\u7855 c ghi.*
